      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car. The exterior finish remains vibrant, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with supple leather upholstery that shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. Every feature, from the power sunroof to the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; I have maintained a comprehensive service log, including a recent oil service and a multi-point inspection that confirmed the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. It handles beautifully with a quiet, smooth ride and no warning lights on the dash. Includes two sets of keys and the original owner's manual.",
